        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Milos Beach &amp; Agios Nikitas, Greece</h2>
        <p>Start by driving along the island's western coast. First you can visit the village of Agios Nikitas and its beautiful beach. From town you have the option of hiking up over the hillside to the much longer <strong>Milos Beach</strong>. Along the 0.9 mile (1.4 km) round-trip hike to Milos Beach you can enjoy great views over the coast.</p>
    </section>


    <!-- Porto Kastsiki Greece Dropdown -->
