        <a class="anchor" id="porto-katsiki"></a>
        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Porto Katsiki &amp; Cape Lefkada</h2>
        <p>Next you can head all the way down the coast of the island to the gorgeous <strong>Porto Katsiki</strong> beach with its towering white cliffs and bright blue waters. You can enjoy incredible views of the beach from the parking lot and get a wider view by taking a short walk to the end of the small peninsula that connects to the parking lot. Be sure to also see this unique beach from below.</p>
        <p>At the very southern tip of the Lefkada Island is <strong>Cape Lefkada</strong>, where you can take in breathtaking panoramic views over the island and its rugged coastline from a charming white lighthouse. The views over the ridge-like southern peninsula are truly amazing.</p>
    </section>



